value.name: 1.003 Centimeters to Millimeters | Convert 1.003 cm in mm - UnitChefs
value.snippet: Usage of fractions is recommended when more precision is needed. If we want to calculate how many Millimeters are 1.003 Centimeters we have to multiply 1.003 by 10 and divide the product by 1. So for 1.003 we have: (1.003 × 10) ÷ 1 = 10.03 ÷ 1 = 10.03 Millimeters. So finally 1.003 cm = 10.03 mm.
